{"tid":1819222,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"區議會中止音樂噴泉工程 政府表示為尊重合約精神及珍惜公帑將會繼續工程","createTime":"2020-01-10T15:15:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-10T17:04:26.000Z","uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"534278117a3e4d7b6fe11c3ad1b2b18b097a3f4a","tid":1819222,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T15:15:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/139543009419663/posts/3728636583843603/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F139543009419663%2Fposts%2F3728636583843603%2F&d=rH9paZ2ORyePGAAUSKfbjVuXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=50e72415\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/139543009419663/posts/3728636583843603/</a><br />\n<br />\n【劉江華：觀塘噴泉及摩頓臺工程將繼續】<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2R4CNNz\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2R4CNNz&d=rH9paZ2ORyePGAAUSKfbjVuXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=e756d2a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/2R4CNNz</a><br />\n<br />\n觀塘及灣仔區議會早前要求煞停已獲財委會通過的 #觀塘音樂噴泉 及灣仔摩頓臺活動中心工程，合共涉及造價1.8億元。<br />\n<br />\n民政事務局局長 #劉江華 表示，該兩項工程已批出合約，為尊重程序及合約精神，以及珍惜公帑，工程將會繼續進行。<br />\n-------------------------------------<br />\n《信報》+《信報月刊》合併訂閱優惠送您《高仁財技&mdash;&mdash;投資自由行》電子書 <br />\n了解更多：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/ejfdncom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fejfdncom&d=rH9paZ2ORyePGAAUSKfbjVuXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=7745a8a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/ejfdncom</a><br />\n<br />\n#信報 #即時新聞 #民政事務局 #觀塘及灣仔區議會"},{"pid":"eb3eadd02c746c579661b92df8a5bcaa523608df","tid":1819222,"uid":1082,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T15:20:31.000Z","msg":"如果張合約寫明係一次過比錢同無得退款既，確認無辦法，只能夠想辦方法去善用呢個設施。<br />\n（同埋區議會要避免再用一筆過付款既工程）<br />\n<br />\n但如果係分期比錢，而個還原錢係少過繼續既錢，咁就要停。"},{"pid":"383cbbd2f2fad2a06dd925acc5607ee49da5313b","tid":1819222,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T15:22:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果張